title._content: The Lone Star (train #15) is shown from the air as it passes a typical rural Oklahoma crossing between guthrie and norman enroute from Chicago to Houston, Texas, June 1974

description._content: Original Caption: The Lone Star (train #15) is shown from the air as it passes a typical rural Oklahoma crossing between guthrie and norman enroute from Chicago to Houston, Texas.
